---

## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.so
*.pyd
*.pyo
*.pkl
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
dist/
build/
site/
.venv/
venv/
.env
.env.*

# --- Jupyter / notebooks ---
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.ipynb_convert/
*.nbconvert.*

# --- Editors / OS ---
.vscode/
.vscode-test/
.idea/
*.code-workspace
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# --- Testing / coverage ---
.coverage
coverage.xml
htmlcov/
.pytest_cache/
.tox/
.mypy_cache/
.dmypy.json
ruff_cache/

# --- Logs / temp ---
*.log
logs/
tmp/
temp/

# --- Data outputs (generated) ---
runs/
output/
results/
figures/
*.fig
*.png
*.pdf

# --- Legacy MATLAB artifacts (if any get copied in) ---
*.m~
*.asv

# --- Local data (keep input profiles in /data, but ignore large raws) ---
data/raw/
*.nc
*.grib
*.grb
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.parquet
*.feather

# --- Secrets (do not commit real secrets) ---
*.key
*.pem
*.crt
secrets.*